                    <h2>For Screen owners</h2>
                    <p>Our philosophy is simple: give the largest chunk of revenues tothe owners of the screen, while we keep a small percentage for takingcare of all the technical and administrative stuff. Getting revenues fromadleria is as simple as creating one or several ad-spaces that describesyour screens and waiting advertisers to start using them. <br><br>

Adleria performs marketing and campaigns to promote yourscreens so that you can get the most it, and you can also easily send alink with your screens to your contacts so that they can directly buy adson them.</p>
