                     <p>Every month you will get a reverse invoice with a detaileddescription of the ads published on your screens and the givenamount of revenue in your bank account. The invoices followsinternational taxation standards so that it becomes super easy for youto account for the revenues.
<br><br>
The revenues are based on the amount of ads that are displayedon your screens. You set yourself the price per impression (animpression is one ad being displayed on a screen), and the amount oftime you want to allow for advertisements (in percentage).</p>
